3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The breakthroughs in AI are mentioned as a reason for the rapid growth in computational chemistry, and the paper utilizes AI techniques for chemical entity extraction. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper involves extracting fine-grained knowledge from publications, which can be considered as a form of information retrieval. 
5. cs.DL (Deep Learning) - The paper utilizes deep learning techniques such as BERT for building the model for scientific data chain extraction.
